{"type": "article", "id": 3127, "title": "MÖKKI  大理石景观灯", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-29T07:25:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232714ImkLcobnTY71FApy.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t墨西哥 PECA 设计工作室的设计师 Caterina Moretti 日前带来一款用大理石做成的景观灯 MÖKKI 。它将灯和花盆融合到一起，花盆和灯罩都采用大理石材质做成，亦有缟玛瑙材质可选，表面均经过了磨砂处理。灯罩里面有 LED 光源，光线透过大理石之后变得更加柔和。整个大理石灯罩形似一座精巧的小房子，而周边的绿植就像是庭院里的小树，构成了一个迷你的庭院景观，显得生趣盎然。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232712C2Y8lLdJ6tcaB7uh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052327127dYqVswxlXiEravo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8296875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232712pz8EHnudFrITMhoX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052327137Y5AZVyxQr8tMsjK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232714sE6bcJPryN7wRafo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}